# StoryLand Driving School — .gitignore
#
# HARD RULE: student PII and secrets NEVER go in this repo.
# If you find yourself typing "git add" on something with student names,
# permit numbers, DOBs, DLs, SSNs, or API keys — STOP.

# ─── Node / build artifacts ───
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
package-lock.json

# ─── OS cruft ───
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~

# ─── Secrets ───
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
secrets.json
credentials.json
*_credentials*
*_secret*
*_token*

# ─── Auto-generated by routines ───
BRIEFING_FLAGS.md

# ─── Student / operational data (never commit) ───
/Students/
/Incidents/
/Legal/
/Recordings/
/Uploads/
/uploads/
*.csv
*-export-*
stripe-export*
twilio-export*
retell-export*
gmail-takeout*

# ─── Vendor statements and PII-bearing PDFs ───
# (the business-planning PDFs you deliberately add are fine; these patterns
# match the accidental drag-and-drop of bank or insurance statements)
/Statements/
/Bank/
/Insurance-claims/
*bank-statement*
*insurance-statement*
*mvr-*
*fingerprint*

# ─── IDE / editor ───
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-*

# ─── Local working copies not meant for the repo ───
/scratch/
/draft/
/local/
